-- London’s New Scotland Yard May Be Sold as Police Reduce Costs
-- B y   C h r i s   S p i l l a n e
-- 2012-10-30T11:46:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-30/london-s-new-scotland-yard-may-be-sold-as-police-reduce-costs.html
New Scotland Yard, the headquarters
of  London ’s police service, may be sold as part of a plan to
reduce costs by 500 million pounds ($803 million), the
Metropolitan Police Authority said. The British Broadcasting
Corp. reported the news earlier today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
